<li>Thinking of you and your family during this incredibly difficult time. Please accept my sincerest condolences.</li>
<li>There are no words to adequately express the sorrow I feel for your loss.  May her memory be a blessing.</li>
<li>Sending you love and strength as you navigate this painful journey.  Your mother's legacy will live on.</li>
<li>I am so deeply saddened by the news of your mother’s passing.  She was a wonderful person.</li>
<li>My heart aches for you and your family. Your mother will be forever in your hearts.</li>
<li>Your mother's kindness and warmth touched so many lives.  She will be dearly remembered.</li>
<li>I’m holding you all in my thoughts and prayers during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sadness I feel at your loss.  May her soul rest in peace.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories of your mother comfort you during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>Please know that I am here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li>Sending you all my love and support.  May your mother's memory be a source of strength.</li>
<li> Your mother was a true inspiration, and her memory will always be treasured.</li>
<li> May the love and support of those around you ease your pain.</li>
    

